---
import '../styles/global.css'
---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/app-icon.png" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="description" content="A multi-pane terminal manager with AI agents built-in. Split, stack, and theme your terminals. Chat with Claude and Codex inline." />
		<title>Terminal GUI - AI-Powered Terminal Manager for macOS</title>
	</head>
	<body class="bg-zinc-950 text-white min-h-screen">
		<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
			<!-- Hero -->
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<img src="/app-icon.png" alt="Terminal GUI" class="w-28 h-28 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-2xl shadow-2xl" />
				<h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-zinc-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
					Terminal GUI
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
					A multi-pane terminal manager with AI agents built-in.<br />
					Split, stack, and theme your terminals. Chat with Claude and Codex inline.
				</p>
				<a
					href="/Terminal-GUI-Installer.dmg"
					download
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white text-zinc-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-zinc-200 transition-colors"
				>
					<svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
					</svg>
					Download for macOS
				</a>
				<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-4">macOS 12+ &middot; Apple Silicon</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Features -->
			<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-20">
				<div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-teal-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-teal-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 5a1 1 0 011-1h14a1 1 0 011 1v2a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V5zM4 13a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6zM16 13a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v6a1 1 0 01-1 1h-2a1 1 0 01-1-1v-6z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Multi-pane Terminals</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">Grid or row layouts with drag-to-reorder. Groups for organizing workspaces. Real shell sessions via native PTY.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-violet-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 10h.01M12 10h.01M16 10h.01M9 16H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V6a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2v8a2 2 0 01-2 2h-5l-5 5v-5z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">AI Agents Inline</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">Claude and Codex chat panes alongside your terminals. Slash commands for code review, refactoring, debugging, and more.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-pink-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-pink-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21a4 4 0 01-4-4V5a2 2 0 012-2h4a2 2 0 012 2v12a4 4 0 01-4 4zm0 0h12a2 2 0 002-2v-4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2.343M11 7.343l1.657-1.657a2 2 0 012.828 0l2.829 2.829a2 2 0 010 2.828l-8.486 8.485M7 17h.01" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Beautiful Themes</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">12 built-in themes including Nord, Dracula, Solarized, and more. Custom theme builder with live preview.</p>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-6">
					<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-500/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
						<svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
							<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
						</svg>
					</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Developer Tools</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-400">Running ports monitor, Claude process manager, real-time WebSocket sync. Everything you need in one place.</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Tech Stack -->
			<div class="text-center mb-16">
				<p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm mb-4">Built with</p>
				<div class="flex justify-center gap-6 flex-wrap">
					<span class="text-zinc-400">Bun</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-600">&middot;</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-400">React 19</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-600">&middot;</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-400">xterm.js</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-600">&middot;</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-400">Tailwind</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-600">&middot;</span>
					<span class="text-zinc-400">Electrobun</span>
				</div>
			</div>

			</main>
	</body>
</html>
